    {
      "id": "80b99be1_cb10bfde",
      "file_path": "a1-policy-management/pom.xml",
      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 259,
      "message": "I found in ONAP nexus that all ccsdk related images have ccsdk as prefix, e.g., ccsdk-cds, ccsdk-apps, ccsdk-dgbuilder etc. \nhttps://nexus3.onap.org/#browse/browse:docker.snapshot:v2%2Fonap\n\nSo, I tried to follow this convention. But if we agree on removing ccsdk from image name, I can do that.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 5051,
        "name": "Muhammad Rehan Raza",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "muhammad.rehan.raza@est.tech",
        "username": "RehanRaza"
      },
      "updated": "2020-07-30 10:09:02.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "22864a4f_fcb554e7",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "id": "99047f70_f8cb3452",
      "file_path": "a1-policy-management/pom.xml",
      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 259,
      "message": "Alright. Because we are into ccsdk, we can have onap/ccsdk-a1policymanagementservice.\nI dont think we need \"oran\" in the image name. whats your thought?",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 3813,
        "name": "Lathishbabu Ganesan",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "lathishbabu.ganesan@est.tech",
        "username": "Lathish"
      },
      "updated": "2020-07-30 10:58:00.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "80b99be1_cb10bfde",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "id": "79ad16f1_946a727a",
      "file_path": "a1-policy-management/pom.xml",
      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 259,
      "message": "I think it would be clear for everyone that this image came from our repo (and repo name is ccsdk/oran). So, in my opinion, it would be better to keep \"oran\" to avoid confusion. \nIf we just have ccsdk-a1policymanagementservice, it would not be clear which repo of ccsdk generated this image.\nFurthermore, all the Jenkinks jobs also have ccsdk-oran as prefix. So, we can relate our staging jobs with the docker image.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 5051,
        "name": "Muhammad Rehan Raza",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "muhammad.rehan.raza@est.tech",
        "username": "RehanRaza"
      },
      "updated": "2020-07-30 11:08:32.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "99047f70_f8cb3452",
      "unresolved": true
    },
